outube.com/watch?v=6cXRFR8Uhl4</a> We need humanitarian aid to protect residents and travelers. <br />\n請自行加減字數。光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"c4e8c1902d1d5e60573bc73150e571e3b2be7437","tid":1348822,"uid":232016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25afd625ab2e1a5f5238e0eddb1feb1b39823c65","tid":1348822,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:03:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2681000ab85c562cd1e839e80b41e2a70384f54","tid":1348822,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:04:01.000Z","msg":"上環"},{"pid":"eb98f1d96dd375a13a3a3717655ceada76806ef1","tid":1348822,"uid":286184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:04:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b69bf773bf91038662af28dcffc20488bc69d920","tid":1348822,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3223540afaaadc0ea7adc0bae4c27a7ce440d642","tid":1348822,"uid":253573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f6f514dce5da4a7baa7547960fbf170b5191db5","tid":1348822,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:04:40.000Z","msg":"[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348028</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7aaea1c85c201fe1246b36224c67bdd4e7745ccf","tid":1348822,"uid":193972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"上環"},{"pid":"b888f8afd43436781ecc2f37eac3c29847be8db8","tid":1348822,"uid":148016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"上環係暴力鎮壓，元朗係恐怖襲擊<br />\n<br />\n元朗班撚屌牛屎佬一撚定清算！同佢合作果班黑渣都係<br />\n但記住我地本來目的係咩先！完左主線再訓身同班牛屎佬，新鴻基全部計！<br />\n<br />\n咪比啲盲毛，三毛輕鬆帶風向，可能第一下你會好嬲但記住<br />\n<br />\n如果懷疑善用起底功能，負皮，上一頁，比有用Post上返黎熱門"},{"pid":"606022d8d31399cab7ee23f1dc6f50c4f01495f0","tid":1348822,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:05:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84ed8e64f560db17ad8a8ef537337e727dd8dab7","tid":1348822,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56b7a11064156a4fd5760cc2a7f18a4360f4a2df","tid":1348822,"uid":232016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4442fd579454105b4fe7f4509d98360888cea7d8","tid":1348822,"uid":244802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674ceeafa6c2b5ded32e330dbc0c5720819c6870","tid":1348822,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:06:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1903b2fe35a7cf431acb3abe67b2f34aca9513e","tid":1348822,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"push!!!!!!1"},{"pid":"d14a951cddeda8fa2909710f1886218e54677d81","tid":1348822,"uid":274774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:26:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26eaeb3d7be50666d323ebcbb124906886fd4362","tid":1348822,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:49:36.000Z","msg":"推，個人認為所有野有番集中post會好啲。<br />\n721集中，記招集中，元朗黑食黑（？）集中⋯太多散post好難推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">721 警黑之夜 - 整合 (上環 + 元朗)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[緊急] 上環義士受傷狀況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347981</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n721 上環開槍整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348232</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n元朗 黑黑相衛 罪狀List，黑材料基地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347791</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩單野係一個局黎，想spin走上環單野！我地要雙軌並行！</span><br />\n721體現警黑合作，香港政權真面目。<br />\n黑警港島三十幾槍，黑社會元朗亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港，時代革命！\n\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"387358a72934422d4e81c2b74ce586a1af607d11","tid":1348822,"uid":60683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18afada125b509c77854c25886ddf81a9119f7a8","tid":1348822,"uid":277263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:50:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d594038816e50d416ae469599ea80a53088c5ff7","tid":1348822,"uid":208894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:50:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fbb783c365805c6a6c1dd841203ad0d6ebed936","tid":1348822,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:52:55.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"108c1e4486bc296b53f67d6d139afe798d54a18b","tid":1348822,"uid":43311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:53:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d9fa482a976166b6ff7b5ca9679