onnect/send-chris-an-email/</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repchrissmith\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepchrissmith&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=391c90e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repchrissmith</a><br />\n<br />\n【十一月】 Ben Cardin<br />\nEmail：<a href=\"https://www.cardin.senate.gov/contact/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cardin.senate.gov%2Fcontact%2F%3F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=4fc39ef5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cardin.senate.gov/contact/?</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatorcardin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatorcardin&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=4826af6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatorcardin</a><br />\n<br />\n【十二月】 James McGovern<br />\nEmail：<a href=\"https://mcgovern.house.gov/contact/zip-auth.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmcgovern.house.gov%2Fcontact%2Fzip-auth.htm&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=5ade6028\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mcgovern.house.gov/contact/zip-auth.htm</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/repmcgovern\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frepmcgovern&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRxvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=1ed862d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/repmcgovern</a><br />\n<br />\n美國媒體清單<br />\n@washingtonpost<br />\n@BBCWorld<br />\n@CBSNews<br />\n@cnni<br />\n@FoxNews<br />\n<br />\n美國總統清單<br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n@VP<br />\n<br />\nTemplate:<br />\nDear Sir/Madam, I am writing as a Hong Kong citizen to inform you of the State Terrorism by the HK government in July 21. The police and triad gangs cooperated to assault citizens. <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cXRFR8Uhl4\" data-sr-url=\"ht